Hey, Read me!

deriv_trading_bot

Quickstart
 - Install deps: pip install -r requirements.txt
 - Run a backtest: python run_backtest.py --csv data/sample_prices.csv

Project layout
 - src/connector.py: placeholder Deriv connector and CSV loader
 - src/strategy.py: SMA crossover strategy
 - src/backtester.py: simple backtester
 - run_backtest.py: example runner
